    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "doctors just keep giving me more pills that don't work or make me feel like a zombie. it's not even about the \"help\" anymore. it's just the thought of finally being able to rest... to just have everything stop. honestly, sometimes it feels like the only kind thing left to do is find some peace.",
