    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's weird hearing you say that. people always tell me i'm being selfish or that i should just try one more thing, but it doesn't feel selfish. it feels like the only logical way to stop the hurting. like, if there was a way to just... turn it off, wouldn't that be the most compassionate thing?",
